{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6f3ad69cd1","title":"虞美人·枕上","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e8c8b4b565","index":0,"year":1921,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"6f3ad69cd1"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji2","name":"毛泽东全集第2卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji2.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji2":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"aff0abe4ce","type":"paragraph","text":"虞美人·枕上","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji2","articleId":"6f3ad69cd1"},{"id":"fdd3e8b3cc","type":"paragraph","text":"（1921年）堆来枕上愁何快，江海翻波浪。夜长天色总难明，假突披衣起坐数寒星。晓来百念都灰尽，叫刺有离人影。一钩残月以向西流，","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji2","articleId":"6f3ad69cd1"},{"id":"38d4eebc89","type":"paragraph","text":"对此不抛眼泪也无由。[I]毛泽东手书句未为问号。2]毛泽东手书句未为问号。[3]毛泽东手书作“无奈披衣起坐寒中”毛泽东手书作“晓来百念皆灰尽”。4]离人，指作者的夫人杨开慧。杨开慧（1901-1930），湖南长沙人，1921年加入中国共产党，在中共酒区委员会负责机要兼交通联络工作，后随作者去上海、武汉等地。1927年大革命失败后，魏蓝在长沙板念坚持地下工作。1930年10月被国民党反动派建描，11月括往。1920年冬，同毛[5]残月，持晓时形状如钩的月亮。宋代悔尧臣《梦后寄欧阳来叔》：“五更千里梦，残月一城鸡。”","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji2","articleId":"6f3ad69cd1"},{"id":"acfcbc98e8","type":"paragraph","text":"0照","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji2","articleId":"6f3ad69cd1"},{"id":"03781ea1a4","type":"paragraph","text":"之","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji2","articleId":"6f3ad69cd1"},{"id":"2bc0c3db03","type":"paragraph","text":"中发鞋住毛泽东手书《虚美人·枕上》战友》（油画挥手从兹去》（油画】","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji2","articleId":"6f3ad69cd1"}],"page":{"id":"085f84c16f","publicationId":"maoquanji2","articleId":"6f3ad69cd1","start":468,"end":470}}}},"__N_SSG":true}